Sager Electronics is an authorized distributor of Saia Burgess.Saia Burgess, part of the Johnson Electric family, is a manufacturer of motors, solenoids, switches, sensors, electronic controllers and subsystems for the automotive, industrial and building automation industries.  Johnson Electric brands distributed by Sager Electronics include Saia Burgess, Ledex and Dormeyer.Click here to visit the Johnson Electric and Ledex websites.












