			Company Description 
		


                Saia, Inc. operates as a transportation holding company, that provides a range of less-than-truckload, non-asset truckload, expedited and logistics services through its wholly-owned subsidiaries across the United States. The company was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Johns Creek, GA.
            




